{"tid":5860,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"李斯特城54年來最差衛冕冠軍","createTime":"2016-11-27T05:49:08.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-27T06:14:00.000Z","uid":10733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a2f6123d2d184755fdcef5737214f433116d0efe","tid":5860,"uid":10733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T05:49:08.000Z","msg":"李斯特城迫和米杜士堡，成功搶得1分，可是13戰得13分的成績，令他們成為英超54年來成績最差的衛冕冠軍。<br />\n李斯特城在歐聯賽場表現可人，可是英超開季至今只贏得3場。<br />\n<br />\n\u0016李斯特城1900萬鎊斟尼迪迪<br />\n<br />\n現時李斯特城13戰得13分，僅比降班區第18位的侯城多2分。而得13分這個成續亦是英格蘭54年來衛冕球隊開季最差成績。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n比李斯特城更差的，只有1962-63年球季的葉士域治，那季他們只得11分 。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n隨此之外，上季李斯特城只有391分鐘落後，但今季到現時為此已有417分鐘，可見他們的退步的確明顯。<br />\n<br />\n不過李斯特城都有好消息，就是陣中主力馬列斯終於回勇，對上3場聯賽射入2球和交出1個助功。(<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=bIjzDQ3e2DTBqJS7sv%2B8y8W%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=381bb35e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>)<br />\n<br />\n比番個盃雲加啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c004785ef92715920c29ecc37c95cb3712b7e88f","tid":5860,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T05:50:35.000Z","msg":"英超54年😱"},{"pid":"2331b23f6dc163d4396187fdde732787f5bc1914","tid":5860,"uid":13320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T06:02:09.000Z","msg":"李城良田未發功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e1df78059070f403d7fd8d9e06038b5f37ce404","tid":5860,"uid":18384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T06:03:09.000Z","msg":"都遇左啦其實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dd88cebb6d82c02cf9a85b38fd0a041c1a4d5c6","tid":5860,"uid":18384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T06:06:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>都遇左啦其實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n預<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 未訓醒"},{"pid":"ffba1e79b56b8643141c07c4cf981fdd8176c72b","tid":5860,"uid":28394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T06:14:00.000Z","msg":"拎左冠軍仲想點<br />\n仲要入埋16強"}]}